5.0.2 (2008/7/14)


--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
ganga/python/GangaAtlas
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Athena:
* ganga-stage-in-out-dq2.py: Fix for disappearing backup-stage-out SEs
* athena-lch.sh: Fix problems with some DPM sites in athena v14 and
  change python32 call behaviour
* BOOT.py/Athena.py: improvements of cmtconfig magic function
* DQ2Dataset.py: Fix wrong return value of get_contents
* DQ2JobSplitter: correctly add input/outputsandbox to the subjob
* DQ2JobSplitter: introduce config['Athena']['MaxJobsDQ2JobSplitter']
  and set the default to 100
* DQ2JobSplitter.py: Add numsubjobs option - now jobs can also be
  splitted by number of subjobs
* Athena.py: Introduce Athena.atlas_exetype, choices: ATHENA, PYARA, ROOT
  Execute the following executable on worker node:
  ATHENA: athena.py jobsOptions input.py
  PYARA: python jobOptions
  ROOT: root -q -b jobOptions
* ganga-stage-in-out-dq2.py: produce now in parallel to input.py also a
  flat file input.txt containing the list of inputfiles. input.txt can be
  read in by PYARA or ROOT application workflow
* Athena.py: Fix bug #38795
* AthenaLocalRTHandler.py: Fix bug #38202
* athena-local.sh: Change setup procedure for ATLAS_PRODUCTION, bug #38802

AthenaMC:
* Bug fix for setup-release.sh: declare environment variable CMTPATH to
  allow derived environment variable LD_LIBRARY_PATH to be set correctly
  by cmt scripts

scripts:
* Protect some variables from setting default values
* Enable multiple inputdataset support: use --inDS dataset1,dataset2
* Change --split and --splitfiles to use DQ2JobSplitter if LCG backend is used
* Add --athena_exe ATHENA or PYARA or ROOT (see above)


